To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private MomentumPercent _momp;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_momp = MOMP(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_momp.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "momentumpercent", _momp.Current.Value);
}
